<subSubSection pageId="92" pageNumber="371" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="92.[176,1382,738,1078]" pageId="92" pageNumber="371">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[179,526,927,960]" pageId="92" pageNumber="371">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The [UCN Red List. Given relatively restricted distribution and lack of biological knowledge, the Costa Rican Harvest Mouse should be carefully monitored.
</paragraph>
